253
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:23,480
Years of auctions have failed to notice Tang Bohu's work.

254
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:27,400
The price should be from millions onwards.

255
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,840
How much? Did you say millions?

256
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:32,600
Millions!

257
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,060
Zhuang Rui,...

258
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,960
...God has heard my thoughts. What did I say before?

259
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,130
When there's a will, there's a way.

260
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:44,760
Millions! 10 million!

261
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:47,720
Increase the price! -Move.

262
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:49,050
Brother,...

263
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:53,520
...I'll pay RMB15 million for this drawing.

264
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:01,480
Sounds fair to me.

265
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,850
Alright. Thank you.

266
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:14,200
If you think it's too little, I'll add more for you.

267
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,020
Brother Ma,...

268
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,200
...if you want this drawing,...

269
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:36,640
...I'll sell it to you for RMB5 million.

270
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,160
Did you say RMB5 million?

271
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:46,080
When I bought this drawing, you gave me RMB3,000.

272
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:49,240
Hence,part of this drawing belongs to you.

273
00:22:49,560 --> 00:22:53,640
Don't. I gave you the money. It's different.

274
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:58,960
If you weren't there, I may not get this drawing.

275
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:01,520
Hence,take it as how I thank you.

276
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:06,160
Brother,this is a big favour.

277
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:11,000
It's hard to see brats like this nowadays.

278
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:15,000
You're realistic and reasonable. Alright. I'll accept this favour.

279
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:18,280
If you need Brother Ma's help for anything,...

280
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:20,920
...I'll be ready anytime. Tell me your account number.

281
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:24,080
I'll transfer the money to you. -About that.....

282
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:25,810
Let me tell you. I know. -No,...

283
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,850
...is it the same for the two of you?

284
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,970
Come here. Sit down and have a chat.

285
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:35,280
The brat is loyal.

286
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:40,480
It's not bad.

287
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:45,140
You're not greedy for money and loyal. I like it.

288
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:51,080
I didn't notice such details about the mounting style.

289
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:52,240
You noticed it.

290
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:55,880
Your eyes are good.

291
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,640
You're really lucky.

292
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:04,880
It's only been half a month, and you found 2 loopholes.

293
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:08,300
It's not too much to say you're the second Feng Quan.

294
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:12,560
I sent the chubby guy away. We'll get RMB5 million.

295
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,360
It supposed to be RMB15 million.

296
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,480
Uncle De,who's Feng Quan?

297
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:22,200
Didn't Pu Song Ling mention someone...

298
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:25,760
...called Feng Quan in a story he wrote in the Strange Tales?

299
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:29,170
He accidentally saved a Trionychidae Fairy.

300
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:32,640
To repay the debt of gratitude, this Trionychidae Fairy...

301
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:35,960
...gave Feng Quan a pair of magical eyes that...

302
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:38,600
...can see all the details and recognise all the treasures.

303
00:24:38,600 --> 00:24:41,400
Since then he's been enjoying his life.

304
00:24:43,360 --> 00:24:46,220
Then Uncle De is right. You're the second Feng Quan.

305
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:56,440
You won't take long to be better than your teacher.

306
00:24:58,520 --> 00:25:00,850
Thank you,Uncle De. -Thank you,Uncle De.

307
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:27,400
Did you really save some Trionychidae Fairy?

308
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:28,920
Do you have a gift now?

309
00:25:30,360 --> 00:25:32,880
What about Trionychidae Fairy and gift? There's no such thing.

310
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:34,340
Then how did you notice...

311
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:36,940
...the gourd that day and the drawing today?

312
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:40,010
They're both based on my instinct.

313
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:45,440
Do you know that I study medicine? I'm materialistic.

314
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:49,400
Do you know materialism? Talk about Trionychidae Fairy.

315
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:52,160
Animals can't become fairy.

316
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:55,160
But I think that...

317
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:57,320
...you can't be compared with that Feng Quan.

318
00:25:57,320 --> 00:26:01,400
You're more incredible than him. We don't need all those... ...magical support.

319
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,400
We still can find loopholes and earn.

320
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:06,160
To me,you're the most incredible god.

321
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:15,040
Didn't Uncle De say that it's fake? It's a novel.

322
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,290
It can't be trusted.

323
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:22,120
We're rich people now.

324
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:26,000
We must learn to be arrogant appropriately.

325
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:29,050
It's only an ancient. Look at how anxious you are.

326
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:36,040
Forget it. I'll... ...buy equipment and play games on my own.

327
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:54,080
It feels good to be rich.

328
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:12,840
I'm having my wedding at Gansu next week. Come if you're free.

329
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,240
Gansu.

330
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:47,570
Boss,...

331
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,850
...you haven't eaten, have you? Come.

332
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:58,240
What are you looking at? It's Chinese Doughnuts.

333
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:01,010
Do you know this?

334
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:04,020
It's sweet. It's really nice.

335
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:07,770
My girlfriend is from Gansu. Her mum often sends it to us.

336
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,160
That's right.

337
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:16,000
I found it from the recording of the car at the opposite side.

338
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:18,800
Do you mean that this gang of people is from Gansu?

339
00:28:24,320 --> 00:28:27,800
By the way,call the Academy of Social Sciences and ask if...

340
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:30,500
...they sent an archaeologist team from Gansu.

341
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,880
Noted. -Wait.

342
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:53,720
Come,have some yoghurt drink. -Thank you.

343
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:58,560
The money from Brother Ma has been transferred.

344
00:28:58,560 --> 00:29:02,320
Aren't you a capable finance manager? You'll handle the money.

345
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:14,040
Don't worry. I'll surely be your useful helper.

346
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,460
Don't do sharing economy anymore this time.

347
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:26,480
I have this. Why do I need to do that? Am I right?

348
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:31,720
By the way,I'm going to Gansu this time.

349
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:34,240
Why are you going to Gansu?

350
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,560
My classmate is getting married. He asked me to go and visit.

351
00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:38,890
Did you say classmate? Is it a guy or a girl?

352
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,200
He was my dorm's big brother.

353
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:46,320
Do you want to join? -Is it Gansu?

354
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:50,320
I'm not interested. You can go ahead on your own.

355
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:52,380
I'll stay at home and guard the house.

356
00:29:53,520 --> 00:29:54,200
That'll do.

357
00:30:02,560 --> 00:30:03,890
What are you looking at?

358
00:30:07,560 --> 00:30:09,290
I want to buy a hiking backpack.

359
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:12,440
After I finished,I want to look at the specs and compare.

360
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,800
Why are you comparing?

361
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:18,040
We're rich people. Choose the most expensive one.

362
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,210
The most expensive one.

363
00:30:26,080 --> 00:30:27,400
Who's that?

364
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:35,560
Hello. -Hi there,is this Mr. Zhuang?

365
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:41,360
Who is this? -Do you remember the...

366
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:44,200
...San He Liu Cricket Gourd?

367
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:48,760
The one with RMB800,000 luxurious car.

368
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:51,240
Ms. Guo Guo.

369
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,060
Please have a seat.

370
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:41,970
About that.....

371
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:43,880
Qin Xuan Bing.

372
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,400
Hello,Ms. Qin.

373
00:31:50,320 --> 00:31:52,050
I've asked you out this time...

374
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:55,220
...to thank you on the cricket you gave me last time.

375
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,160
I like it a lot. Thank you.

376
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:02,680
It's not an expensive gift. It's so much worse than the gourd.

377
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:05,900
Actually,I don't know much about antiques.

378
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:10,760
But the cricket reminded me a lot about the past.

379
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:16,160
My father gave me a cricket when I was young.

380
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:20,680
It was summer that year when he took the meal worms with me,...

381
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:24,640
...fed it and played with it. We listened to it.

382
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:29,690
It's the most beautiful gift I've ever received.

383
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:44,320
This is the right gift then. -A cricket.

384
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,640
Did you make this?

385
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:55,880
Crickets are also called '100-day-insect'.

386
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:59,280
Their lives are short. They can't live past Winter Solstice.

387
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:01,980
But the joy that crickets bring to people...

388
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,240
...will always stay.

389
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,920
Thank you. I will keep it properly.

390
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:21,120
Ms. Qin,would you like to have a drink?

391
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:26,600
It's not early now. Let's return.

392
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:28,540
Let me send you.

393
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:34,200
You must have driven here yourself.

394
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:38,600
No,actually I don't live far.

395
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:41,810
I'm staying at the hotel apartment opposite.

396
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,000
You.....

397
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:55,460
Why don't you speak first? -Are you studying antiques?

398
00:33:55,760 --> 00:33:58,560
The San He Liu Gourd was wrapped around so thickly.

399
00:33:58,560 --> 00:34:02,840
But you could tell. -I'm a history student.

400
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,920
I worked in a pawn shop for a year.

401
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:12,670
What about you? -I'm learning jewellery design.

402
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:14,320
Is it about diamonds?

403
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:16,920
And some jades and emeralds too.

404
00:34:18,630 --> 00:34:21,630
Then you can be counted as half-involved in antiques.

405
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:22,080
Nope.

406
00:34:28,480 --> 00:34:32,670
My workshop is in front. Why not have some coffee there?

407
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:35,670
Sure. Are we drinking coffee again?

408
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,320
Bing Bing,...

409
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:44,150
...where have you been? I've been waiting for half a day.

410
00:34:44,150 --> 00:34:47,800
Mr. Zhuang gave me a cricket last time.

411
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,840
I want to buy him a cup of coffee to thank him.

412
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,480
Yes,you must thank him.

413
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,480
Let's go. I'll send you back.

414
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:01,240
It's fine. I have something on in my office. I must return.

415
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:06,480
Alright. Then let me send Mr. Zhuang back.

416
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:09,680
I must thank him. I'll leave you. -Alright.

417
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:23,280
I can walk on my own. -Get in the car.

418
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,680
Get in the car.

419
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,520
Cook's Rose from 2009.

420
00:35:56,880 --> 00:36:00,680
Bing Bing drinks wine from areas involved in champagne production.

421
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:04,020
Are you interested? If you are, I can give you 2 bottles.

422
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:10,730
My family and Bingbing's family are friends.

423
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:14,250
She just came to Beijing. She doesn't have much friends.

424
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:17,760
Her father has told me to take good care of her.

425
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:23,560
I wanted her to live at the Quadrangle next to Hu Palace.

426
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:26,280
Who'd have thought that she has chosen this place.

427
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,740
She said that this place has artistic vibes.

428
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:32,450
It's only 400-square foot. It must be suffering for her.

429
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:35,200
Is she used to staying at such a big place alone?

430
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:38,480
Of course. She has 2 full-time nannies.

431
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:41,900
And I come and see her every day. Why is she not used to it?

432
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:45,760
By the way,about the cricket,...

433
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:48,760
...I want to thank you on behalf of Bing Bing.

434
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,920
We've cleared the debts of our transaction.

435
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:54,280
There shouldn't be much related after this.

436
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:10,600
We're here. -How are we here?

437
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:16,400
There're subway trains,buses, and car sharing services in front.

438
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:18,090
You can go ahead.

439
00:37:42,040 --> 00:37:42,520
What?

440
00:37:47,160 --> 00:37:49,120
So,you didn't go up,did you?

441
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:56,680
That's a pity. She offered for you to go.

442
00:37:58,520 --> 00:38:01,720
She invited me to her drawing room. There's nothing else.

443
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:02,720
I know.

444
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:07,680
You can be disappointed. But don't be regretful.

445
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:11,320
They're from the royal family. We're upstarts.

446
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:15,160
That's right. We're softshell turtles in their eyes.

447
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:17,440
They won't be nice to you sincerely.

448
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:20,760
I didn't think that much.

449
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,720
Yes. They're rich.

450
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:29,280
But they aren't happy. Look. Since they're born,...

451
00:38:29,280 --> 00:38:33,600
...they have everything. They don't feel things anymore.

452
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:36,320
Even a lousy cricket makes her happy. They're not like us.

453
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:41,920
Our lives are colourful. There are ups and downs.

454
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:45,800
Look at what we experienced. It's like a roller coaster ride.

455
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,880
Do you know what are wines from areas that produce champagnes?

456
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:52,080
Yes. What?

457
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:55,120
Wines from areas that produce champagnes.

458
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:04,680
Her friend said that Ms. Qin likes wines from those places.

459
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:09,000
These ladies are hypocritical.

460
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:11,320
No,why do you care about her?

461
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:14,520
You won't see her anymore. Am I right?

462
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:19,680
By the way,I bought you flight tickets to Gansu.

463
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:23,680
It's business class, but it's discounted.

464
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:28,040
You said it yourself. Although we're rich,...

465
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:30,000
...we can't waste,isn't it?

466
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:47,250
Zhuang Rui,you can see clearly without glasses now?

467
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:55,400
I simply brought it up in the chat group. You really came.

468
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:59,640
I'm taking my visit to your wedding as travelling.

469
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:01,840
I wanted to hold it at Lanzhou.

470
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:04,820
But my father insists on coming back to the village.

471
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,640
This is too far away. It's so isolated.

472
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:11,340
My wife is not willing to come back at all.

473
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:14,980
It's the old people's tradition. Just give in for a bit.

474
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,880
This is my cousin,Er Mao.

475
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:20,680
Hello. -Hello.

476
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:24,440
If I'm busy entertaining relatives these 2 days,...

477
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,300
...ask Er Mao to bring you around.

478
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:29,360
There's an archaeologist team in the village.

479
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:32,000
If you're interested,ask Er Mao to bring you and have a look.

480
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:34,860
After all,you're the only one doing our old job now.

481
00:40:48,120 --> 00:40:50,160
Careful. Make sure it's straight.

482
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:53,010
Careful. Make it straight. That's right.

483
00:40:53,400 --> 00:40:54,600
Don't let them touch.

484
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:01,180
Hold on.

485
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,660
What are you in-charge of?

486
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:06,320
I heard that an archaeologist team...

487
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,720
...were doing some work, I came to see.

488
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:12,520
Kid,how can you come as you like?
